content: Iron Man is a 2008 American superhero film based on the Marvel Comics character of the same name. Iron Man is a superhero appearing in American comic books published by Marvel Comics.
title: Iron Man

content: Captain America: The First Avenger is a 2011 American superhero film based on the Marvel Comics character Captain America.
title: Captain America

content: Spider-Man is a superhero created by writer-editor Stan Lee and writer-artist Steve Ditko.
title: Spider Man
